{"tid":397181,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"DxOMark最新版手機相機拍照排名出爐","createTime":"2017-09-12T09:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T00:38:42.000Z","uid":23677,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05ed62b1342aa02473ce79797ca7268942dfac37","tid":397181,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"最近，專業相機測評機構 DxOMark 發佈了最新的手機相機排名，在排名中，HTC 10 與三星 Galaxy S7 Edge 並列第一，評分為 88 分（滿分為 100 分），Moto Z Force 以 87 分位列第三。 iPhone 6s Plus 得到了 84 分，排在第 9 位。<br />\n<br />\nDxOMark 成立於 2003 年，可以算得上是目前世界上最專業的相機測試機構之一。最早 DxOMark 是透過測試儀和計算公式，來對相機生成的 RAW 格式進行評估，換句話說，就是一開始是做相機評測的。<br />\n<br />\n近幾年，DxOMark 也開始做了手機拍照的評分，但不少人發現，每年的評分排行中，隨便在搜尋平台一搜，總能看到一些和一般人預期不太一樣的結果，比如：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">硬體軟體工具一樣的三星 Galaxy S6 edge 和 Note 5 為什麼會有不一樣的評分？<br />\n本來 iPhone 6s 拍照品質還不錯，可是為什麼連前 10 都排不上。<br />\nSony手機的評分怎麼會那麼高？<br />\n拍照評分究竟可不可靠，評分高的手機就能拍出好看照片嗎？</div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/44867-dxomark-latest-version-camera-rankings-released-iphone-6s-plus-ranked-9th\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F44867-dxomark-latest-version-camera-rankings-released-iphone-6s-plus-ranked-9th&d=%2Foq5WVFsgko3n0FKNOjHdf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f1dd887a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/44867-dxomark-latest-version-camera-rankings-released-iphone-6s-plus-ranked-9th</a>"},{"pid":"a2b389f51f7d659cb8ee7e3fa93e8e95a6f318e5","tid":397181,"uid":23677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dxomark.com/introducing-the-new-dxomark-mobile-test-protocol/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dxomark.com%2Fintroducing-the-new-dxomark-mobile-test-protocol%2F&d=%2Foq5WVFsgko3n0FKNOjHdf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=90ef411a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dxomark.com/introducing-the-new-dxomark-mobile-test-protocol/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m693oxp1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm693oxp1&h=a851c50a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e3519ce41ea073e51b1c137d8114d3d1f148e3e","tid":397181,"uid":146102,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"257c59961120be8f495a53ce1fab498ddd101914","tid":397181,"uid":23677,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><del>hello，我係AB<br />\n<br />\n$106月費已經有4G 21MB<br />\n$166月費有6GB全速4G<br />\n$236月費有全速4.5G 12GB<br />\n用Smart one網絡 <br />\n唔洗再捱貴plan！<br />\n<br />\n仲另有家居寬頻（公居屋、私樓、村屋）！<br />\nTG: hkbnalab<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkbnalab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkbnalab&d=%2Foq5WVFsgko3n0FKNOjHdf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=53a9ac56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkbnalab</a></del></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7642964ec64d4b7ad7e619e8312d6cb0ba3c2b1","tid":397181,"uid":51584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"nokia 808先61分？"},{"pid":"8501749364243f7058de3735cd0703098db6b463","tid":397181,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2697ae3e87e12d0dd3c3ac1b123275cb97fbd57","tid":397181,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解pixel會同u11同分</blockquote><br />\nPixel影黃昏屌打all"},{"pid":"6c063844c4ebd53fca73808993ed83f67f1d035b","tid":397181,"uid":12933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>nokia 808先61分？</blockquote><br />\n可能低光源下唔夠好"},{"pid":"1e9fd03c84552200b7da5a858dbb929f071d9fbc","tid":397181,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:24:05.000Z","msg